\begin{rSection}{Software Packages and Databases}

\begin{rList}
\item Thue-Mahler equation solver and $S$-unit equation solver via a Tzanakis-de Weger approach\\
Available at \verb+https://www.nt.math.ubc.ca/BeGhRe/+\\

\item Goormaghtigh equation solver\\
Available at \verb+https://www.nt.math.ubc.ca/BeGhKr/+\\

\item An efficient Thue-Mahler equation solver via Weil heights\\
In preparation.\\

\item Elliptic curves over $\mathbb{Q}$ of conductor $N < 10^6$ database\\
In preparation.

\end{rList}
\end{rSection}

